{"tid":1077441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國承諾開放經濟，以期結束貿易戰","createTime":"2019-03-25T14:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T04:49:31.000Z","uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"da04fdbc7e839420a87d9ff46af4d940bb188e47","tid":1077441,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T14:52:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/business/20190325/china-trade-xi/zh-hant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fbusiness%2F20190325%2Fchina-trade-xi%2Fzh-hant&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=08bdf357\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/business/20190325/china-trade-xi/zh-hant</a><br />\n北京&mdash;&mdash;中國最高經濟決策者本週承諾，中國準備向更多市場化的競爭和國際貿易開放經濟。這是中國結束與美國之間數十億美元貿易戰強烈意願的最新跡象。"},{"pid":"22ddd983fe5924ea11d684d43300a2f403fe07f4","tid":1077441,"uid":39855,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:37:31.000Z","msg":"重點係，對現到先叫承諾！"},{"pid":"625cba8d05a6eddc6436911a50e489d715601a56","tid":1077441,"uid":150347,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:39:36.000Z","msg":"人地係要你實踐，唔係承諾，又遊花園<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684a8843b9dc6f8b8161b3bed3a073df90bf8902","tid":1077441,"uid":49197,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:40:08.000Z","msg":"開放經濟=經濟會越黎越發達,又可以借D意買多D美國高質素產品<br />\n結論:中國又贏"},{"pid":"6bdd4aff70b4da6b02f2edff3a597a3bdbfe370c","tid":1077441,"uid":141151,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:40:39.000Z","msg":"英國研究<br />\n台灣報導<br />\n南韓起源<br />\n北韓宣布<br />\n美國情報<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國承諾</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c48bb9c458836419d5d78dba51832f14863ceb05","tid":1077441,"uid":76745,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15: